32:27.167 --> 32:29.201
Right, Susan?

32:30.533 --> 32:32.600
I spoke to Kate and Dori.

32:32.667 --> 32:34.800
I think you need to talk to your dad.

32:34.867 --> 32:37.368
I think he deserves the truth.

32:42.101 --> 32:44.400
There's stuff I haven't told you.

32:48.667 --> 32:50.934
Hey, you guys.

32:51.001 --> 32:52.667
Is your mom home?

32:55.167 --> 32:56.667
Catherine...

32:59.368 --> 33:02.167
Hello, Ms. Foster, Mr. Loker.

33:02.234 --> 33:04.268
I called the IRS today.

33:04.334 --> 33:06.734
They assured me that you
wouldn't overstep your bounds,

33:06.800 --> 33:08.734
that they'd hate to see my civil rights violated.

33:08.800 --> 33:11.500
But I'm sure that that's not your intention.

33:11.567 --> 33:12.967
Of course not.

33:14.433 --> 33:18.834
I can see that you have a
fondness for children, Gillian,

33:18.901 --> 33:21.101
