from you is misdirected at me.

33:27.301 --> 33:31.567
My seed flourishes...

33:31.634 --> 33:33.467
Hey, buddy.

33:35.834 --> 33:40.268
While yours, well, doesn't.

33:44.167 --> 33:45.301
I can help you.

33:45.368 --> 33:46.901
You and I can pray together.

33:46.967 --> 33:48.867
Many of the female members

33:48.934 --> 33:50.767
couldn't conceive in the outside world,

33:50.834 --> 33:53.500
but when they came here, we prayed,

33:53.567 --> 33:55.134
and they conceived.

33:55.201 --> 33:58.934
Your problem isn't biological. It's spiritual.

33:59.001 --> 34:02.034
I don't need you to help me pray.

34:02.101 --> 34:04.034
Today's the last day of your court order.

34:04.101 --> 34:07.500
Gather your things. You're
no longer welcome here.

34:11.867 --> 34:14.766
He must have looked you
up online or something.

34:14.833 --> 34:19.034
It's a cold read. It's a carnival trick.

34:22.734 --> 34:25.101
Ok.

34:25.167 --> 34:29.433
I've taken all the facts of
this case into consideration.

34:29.500 --> 34:32.067
And I've decided to drop all
charges against Cabe McNeil.

34:32.134 --> 34:33.268
What?

34:33.333 --> 34:35.400
I'm sorry, but the extenuating circumstances

34:35.467 --> 34:36.600
of this case are such...

34:36.667 --> 34:38.333
He violated my daughter.
I mean, she's a kid.

34:38.400 --> 34:40.167
He's a 22-year-old man.

34:40.234 --> 34:41.766
He had a reasonable belief
that she was of age.

34:41.833 --> 34:44.867
It was filmed! It's out in the world forever!

34:44.934 --> 34:47.001
The only one who gets punished is my daughter?

34:47.067 --> 34:48.167
Come on!

34:48.234 --> 34:49.333
Mr. Reed. It was a tough decision.

34:49.400 --> 34:50.967
Oh, this is the way the system always works.

34:51.034 --> 34:54.001
You're the prosecutor. Do your job!

34:54.067 --> 34:57.134
The system has to make someone pay.

34:57.201 --> 34:59.634
My job gives me prosecutorial discretion,

34:59.700 --> 35:01.134
and I am using it here.

35:01.201 --> 35:03.934
Your daughter went to the party
with intent of having sex.

35:04.001 --> 35:05.368
She lied about her age.

35:05.433 --> 35:06.634
She filmed it.

35:06.700 --> 35:08.034
She's the victim!

35:08.101 --> 35:10.901
In this case, Cabe McNeil is a victim, too.

35:13.101 --> 35:15.433
Come on, Susan.

35:17.167 --> 35:19.067
Excuse me.

35:19.134 --> 35:21.533
Jay, I don't know what to say.

35:21.600 --> 35:23.134
How about "I'm sorry"?

35:23.201 --> 35:26.433
Could you please get my
daughter's jacket now? Now?

35:28.934 --> 35:30.600
I'm not a bigot, Zoe.

35:30.667 --> 35:32.067
