35:37.467 --> 35:39.867
Hey, Jay, I am sorry.

35:39.934 --> 35:41.533
Good job on the case.

35:41.600 --> 35:43.934
Next time, I'm knocking you in the dirt.

35:44.001 --> 35:46.433
Mr. Reed. Hold on a minute.

35:46.500 --> 35:48.800
Hold on. Hold on a sec.

35:50.634 --> 35:53.234
I think I know what you're going to do.

35:53.301 --> 35:55.001
I'm fine now.

35:55.067 --> 35:57.101
Yeah, well, your hand says otherwise.

35:57.167 --> 36:01.167
Look, don't go off to Cabe, all right?

36:01.234 --> 36:04.533
It will just make matters worse for yourself.

36:04.600 --> 36:06.467
Think about your daughter.

36:10.368 --> 36:13.001
She's all I'm thinking about.

36:24.533 --> 36:25.967
I thought you were done.

36:26.034 --> 36:27.467
Well, we just have a couple more questions.

36:27.533 --> 36:28.967
Actually, just one more question.

36:29.034 --> 36:30.700
Are you ready to leave?

36:30.767 --> 36:34.301
Whoa. Whoa, whoa, whoa. What's going on?

36:34.368 --> 36:36.201
You need to leave here
before Jamie sees us.

36:37.767 --> 36:40.368
No, actually...

36:40.433 --> 36:42.700
I want you to leave.

36:42.767 --> 36:43.800
What is that?

36:43.867 --> 36:45.134
It's a safehouse.

36:45.201 --> 36:46.600
It's a licensed non-profit for battered women.

36:46.667 --> 36:48.834
They'll take you and your children
and get you out of here

36:48.901 --> 36:49.867
and find you a place to stay,

36:49.934 --> 36:51.368
and they will never reveal your location...

36:51.433 --> 36:52.533
Are you out of your mind?

36:52.600 --> 36:53.967
He'll find me.

36:54.034 --> 36:55.467
He'll bring me back and make me a prisoner.

36:55.533 --> 36:57.201
You already are a prisoner.

36:57.268 --> 36:59.334
You're helping her kidnap the man's children.

36:59.400 --> 37:00.634
That is not the way to do this, Foster.

37:00.700 --> 37:02.467
The van's leaving in 30 seconds.

37:02.533 --> 37:04.734
Come on. It's your last chance.

37:06.567 --> 37:08.500
I'm going with or without you,

37:08.567 --> 37:10.101
