37:10.167 --> 37:11.667
Come on, guys.

37:15.034 --> 37:16.734
Thank you.

37:16.800 --> 37:18.734
Go around.

37:18.800 --> 37:21.101
Come on, guys. Around the car, ok?

37:22.400 --> 37:24.667
Hey! Hey!

37:24.734 --> 37:27.567
Catherine, what are you doing?

37:27.634 --> 37:29.967
Those are my children, Catherine!

37:30.034 --> 37:33.500
Don't... Catherine! Catherine, stay here!

37:33.567 --> 37:36.201
