with Catherine's departure.

38:03.034 --> 38:05.201
Mr. Cowley tells a different story.

38:05.268 --> 38:08.867
Mr. Cowley believes he's
a prophet sent from God.

38:08.934 --> 38:10.767
He's delusional.

38:10.834 --> 38:12.934
You don't play games with the IRS.

38:15.268 --> 38:16.967
Mr. Loker, um,

38:17.034 --> 38:18.867
You've been very quiet.

38:18.934 --> 38:20.967
