38:57.101 --> 38:59.034
Why did you do that?

38:59.101 --> 39:00.967
Well, you got to have faith in something.

39:01.034 --> 39:02.834
I'm putting mine in you.

39:02.901 --> 39:06.201
Thank you.

39:06.268 --> 39:08.800
Doesn't mean what you did was right.

39:08.867 --> 39:10.901
Boss needs you in the lab.

39:10.967 --> 39:12.867
I'll be right there.

39:17.400 --> 39:18.734
She's a kid!

