Oh, thanks. I appreciate that.

39:22.234 --> 39:23.567
Um, Reynolds called in a favor.

39:23.634 --> 39:25.433
He's got a cop watching Cabe.

39:25.500 --> 39:28.034
Hey, what's going on?

39:28.101 --> 39:29.800
