39:53.967 --> 39:55.400
All right. Just play it again. Play it again.

39:55.467 --> 39:56.901
No, no, no. Let it play. Let it play.

39:56.967 --> 39:58.368
Make someone pay.

39:58.433 --> 40:00.901
Listen to his words.

40:00.967 --> 40:02.567
The system is at fault.

40:02.634 --> 40:04.901
"The system has to make someone pay."

40:04.967 --> 40:06.867
Oh, hell.
