42:05.234 --> 42:08.467
How did all of this get so messed up?

42:08.533 --> 42:12.901
See, this is what I mean
about consequences, love.

42:12.967 --> 42:14.901
Can't predict them.

42:14.967 --> 42:18.167
And when it comes
to you,

42:18.234 --> 42:20.134
